data.description: Welcome to 38 Jane Drive. This lovely 3 Bedroom solid brick Ranch home is centrally located near shopping and schools. Enjoy the ease of one floor living. The Living Room is filled with natural light from the large picture window and boasts Hardwood Floors. The 3 spacious Bedrooms are freshly painted and also have Hardwood Floors. The Spacious Eat-in Kitchen provides plenty of room for cooking and entertaining. The Basement includes a full Bathroom. Outside you will find a large private backyard and a patio. Roof 2009, windows replaced 2014, cook-top 2023
